AxCalculatedMeasure.Name: AverageDaysLate
AxCalculatedMeasure.HelpText: Average difference from expected delivery to actual product receipt for all late product receipts
AxCalculatedMeasure.Label: @SYS343819
AxCalculatedMeasure.Expression: CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[AverageDaysLate] AS IIF( ISEMPTY(([ProductReceiptLines].[PrecisionOfDelivery].&[2], [Measures].[ProductReceiptLinesCount])) OR ([ProductReceiptLines].[PrecisionOfDelivery].&[2], [Measures].[ProductReceiptLinesCount]) = 0, NULL, ([Measures].[DaysLate] / ([ProductReceiptLines].[PrecisionOfDelivery].&[2], [Measures].[ProductReceiptLinesCount])) ), VISIBLE = 1;

AxCalculatedMeasure.Name: AverageDaysEarly
AxCalculatedMeasure.HelpText: Average difference from expected delivery to actual product receipt for all early product receipts
AxCalculatedMeasure.Label: @GLS180356
AxCalculatedMeasure.Expression: CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[AverageDaysEarly] AS IIF( ISEMPTY(([ProductReceiptLines].[PrecisionOfDelivery].&[0], [Measures].[ProductReceiptLinesCount])) OR ([ProductReceiptLines].[PrecisionOfDelivery].&[0], [Measures].[ProductReceiptLinesCount]) = 0, 0, ([Measures].[DaysEarly] / ([ProductReceiptLines].[PrecisionOfDelivery].&[0], [Measures].[ProductReceiptLinesCount])) ), VISIBLE = 1;

AxCalculatedMeasure.Name: VendorPerformanceOnProductReceiptsPercentLate
AxCalculatedMeasure.HelpText: Percent of all product receipts where the product receipt lines are received late
AxCalculatedMeasure.Label: @GLS180355
AxCalculatedMeasure.Expression:
CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[VendorPerformanceOnProductReceiptsPercentLate] AS IIF ( IsEmpty ( [Measures].[ProductReceiptLinesCount] ) OR [Measures].[ProductReceiptLinesCount] = 0 OR IsEmpty ( ( [Measures].[ProductReceiptLinesCount] ,[ProductReceiptLines].[PrecisionOfDelivery].&[2] ) ) OR ( [Measures].[ProductReceiptLinesCount] ,[ProductReceiptLines].[PrecisionOfDelivery].&[2] ) = 0
,0 ,Round ( 100 * ( [Measures].[ProductReceiptLinesCount] ,[ProductReceiptLines].[PrecisionOfDelivery].&[2] ) / ( [Measures].[ProductReceiptLinesCount] ,[ProductReceiptLines].[PrecisionOfDelivery].[All] ) ,2 ) );

,0 ,Round ( 100 * ( [Measures].[ProductReceiptLinesCount] ,[ProductReceiptLines].[PrecisionOfDelivery].&[1] ) / ( [Measures].[ProductReceiptLinesCount] ,[ProductReceiptLines].[PrecisionOfDelivery].[All] ) ,2 ) );

,0 ,Round ( 100 * ( [Measures].[ProductReceiptLinesCount] ,[ProductReceiptLines].[PrecisionOfDelivery].&[0] ) / ( [Measures].[ProductReceiptLinesCount] ,[ProductReceiptLines].[PrecisionOfDelivery].[All] ) ,2 ) );

AxCalculatedMeasure.Name: PurchaseLineAverageDaysFromFirstConfirmationToReceived
AxCalculatedMeasure.HelpText: Average difference from first confirmation to the last product receipt registered
AxCalculatedMeasure.Label: @GLS180513
AxCalculatedMeasure.Expression: CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[PurchaseLineAverageDaysFromFirstConfirmationToReceived] AS IIF( IsEmpty([Measures].[PurchaseLinesCount]) OR [Measures].[PurchaseLinesCount] = 0, NULL, [Measures].[PurchaseLineTotalDaysFromFirstConfirmationToReceived] / [Measures].[PurchaseLinesCount] ), VISIBLE = 1;

AxCalculatedMeasure.Name: PurchaseLineAverageDaysLateFromFirstRequestedDeliveryDateToReceived
AxCalculatedMeasure.HelpText: Average difference from the requested delivery date of first confirmation to the last product receipt registered for purchase lines with late receipt
AxCalculatedMeasure.Label: @GLS180514
AxCalculatedMeasure.Expression: CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[PurchaseLineAverageDaysLateFromFirstRequestedDeliveryDateToReceived] AS IIF( IsEmpty([Measures].[PurchaseLinesCount]) OR [Measures].[PurchaseLinesCount] = 0, NULL, ([PurchaseLines].[PrecisionOfReceiptBasedOnRequestedDeliveryDateOnFirstConfirmation].&[2],[Measures].[PurchaseLineTotalDaysFromFirstRequestedDeliveryDateToReceived]) / ([PurchaseLines].[PrecisionOfReceiptBasedOnRequestedDeliveryDateOnFirstConfirmation].&[2],[Measures].[PurchaseLinesCount]) ), VISIBLE = 1;

AxCalculatedMeasure.Name: PurchaseLineAverageDaysEarlyFromFirstRequestedDeliveryDateToReceived
AxCalculatedMeasure.HelpText: >Average difference from the requested delivery date of first confirmation to the last product receipt registered for purchase lines with early receipt
AxCalculatedMeasure.Label: @GLS180515
AxCalculatedMeasure.Expression: CREATE MEMBER CURRENTCUBE.[PurchaseLineAverageDaysEarlyFromFirstRequestedDeliveryDateToReceived] AS IIF( IsEmpty([Measures].[PurchaseLinesCount]) OR [Measures].[PurchaseLinesCount] = 0, NULL, ABS(([PurchaseLines].[PrecisionOfReceiptBasedOnRequestedDeliveryDateOnFirstConfirmation].&[0],[Measures].[PurchaseLineTotalDaysFromFirstRequestedDeliveryDateToReceived]) / ([PurchaseLines].[PrecisionOfReceiptBasedOnRequestedDeliveryDateOnFirstConfirmation].&[0],[Measures].[PurchaseLinesCount])) ), VISIBLE = 1;
